<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>New website coming soon</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex">
    <meta name="MSSmartTagsPreventParsing" content="true">
    <meta http-equiv="expires" content="0">
    <meta http-equiv="Cache-control" content="no-cache">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="data:image/ico;base64,">
    <style type="text/css">
html {
  margin:0; padding:0; border:0;
	position:relative;
	min-height:100%;
	height:100%;
	font-family: Trebuchet MS,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Tahoma,sans-serif;
	-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
	-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
	background-color:#EBEBEB;
}

body {
  margin:0; padding:0; border:0;
	position:relative;
	min-height:100%;
	height:100%;
	color:#444444;
	line-height:1.2em;
}
header {
  position:relative;
  background:#8C89A9;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse at center top, #C1C0D3 0%, #8C89A9 100%);
  font-size:3em;
  font-size:8vw;
  font-weight:bold;
  line-height:8vw;
  color:#FFFFFF;
  text-shadow:0px 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  text-align:center;
  padding:4% 8%;
  border-bottom:8px solid #777777;
}

main {
  padding:0 2%;
}

h1 {
  text-align:center;
  margin:6% 0;
  font-size:2.0em;
  line-height:1.2em;
}

footer {
  box-sizing:border-box;
  position:absolute;
  bottom:0;
  width:100%;
  background:#AAAAAA;
  color:#666666;
  text-align:right;
  padding:4px 12px;
  font-size:0.8em;
}
footer a { color:#555577; }
footer a:hover { color:#222277; }

    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header>
      New website<br>coming soon
    </header>
    <main>
      <h1>No content has been uploaded yet.</h1>

      <p>If you are the owner of this website: just upload a start page (eg. <code>index.html</code> or <code>index.php</code>) to your webspace, then this message will disappear.</p>

    </main>
    <footer>
      Powered by <a href="http://www.liveconfig.com">LiveConfig® Hosting Control Panel</a>
    </footer>
  </body>
  <script type="text/javascript">
    var msg = {
      cs: [ 'Těšte se na<br>nové stránky', 'Žádný obsah nebyl dosud uploadován.', 'Jste-li majitelem této webové stránky: uploadujte startovací stránku (např.  <code>index.html</code> nebo <code>index.php</code>) do Vašeho webového prostoru, a toto upozornění zmizí.' ],
      de: [ 'Hier entsteht eine<br>neue Website', 'Es wurden noch keine Inhalte hochgeladen.', 'Wenn Sie der Betreiber dieser Website sind: laden Sie einfach eine Startseite (z.B. <code>index.html</code> oder <code>index.php</code>) auf Ihren Webspace, dann wird diese Meldung nicht mehr angezeigt.' ],
      es: [ 'Nueva página<br>en preparación', 'No se ha subido ningún contenido todavía.', 'Si eres el dueño de este sitio web: sencillamente sube una página de inicio (p. ej. <code>index.html</code> o <code>index.php</code>) a su espacio web y enseguida desaparecerá el aviso.' ],
      nl: [ 'Hier verschijnt binnenkort<br>een nieuwe website', 'Er is nog geen inhoud beschikbaar gesteld.', 'Als u de eigenaar van deze website bent, dan kunt u gewoon een start pagina (b.v. <code>index.html</code> of <code>index.php</code>) naar uw webruimte uploaden en dan zal deze mededeling verdwijnen.' ]
    };
    var languages = [ navigator.language || navigator.userLanguage || navigator.browserLanguage || navigator.systemLanguage || 'en' ];
    var accept_lang = '<!--#echo var="HTTP_ACCEPT_LANGUAGE" -->';
    if (accept_lang.length > 0 && !accept_lang.match(/^<!--/)) languages = accept_lang.replace(/;[^,]*/g,'').split(/,/);
    if (navigator.languages) languages = navigator.languages;
    for (i=0; i<languages.length; i++) {
      var lang=languages[i].replace(/-.*/g,'');
      if (msg[lang]) {
        document.getElementsByTagName('header')[0].innerHTML=msg[lang][0];
        document.getElementsByTagName('h1')[0].innerHTML=msg[lang][1];
        document.getElementsByTagName('p')[0].innerHTML=msg[lang][2];
        document.title=msg[lang][0].replace(/<br>/,' ');
        break;
      }
    }
  </script>
</html>
